title: Quicheria
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, Catering, European, French
description: A pleasant cafe/restaurant which offers a wide range of vegan quiches (approximately half of the menu) in different sizes, along with other vegan choices such as salads, a breakfast menu, sandwiches, hot & cold drinks, and  tarts in different sizes. Has a friendly and relaxed ambiance. In addition to the menu, you can choose the ingredients you want for your quiche or tart and they'll make it for you. All food is Kosher. Has gluten free items. Tel Aviv area.
